data.description:
Beautiful Older 2-Story Home with 3-Large Bdrms  &  1.5 baths.
Main level is very Open with Formal Dining Room, living room and 4-seasons room w/fireplace & hardwood floors.  Large Eat-in Kitchen w/Breakfast Bar, heated floor &lots of storage.  Main Floor Laundry and Large Mudroom/Back Porch with built in cabinets.  3-Stall Garage + Shed for all toys and tinkering.
